Mathlib review and triage dashboard

Welcome to the mathlib review and triage dashboard. This is a prototype for better exposing the currently open PRs to mathlib. Feedback (including bug reports and ideas for improvements) on this dashboard is very welcome, for instance directly on the github repository.
This dashboard was last updated on: March 03, 2025 at 15:33 UTC

Quick links: PR statistics | queue | queue-new-contributors | queue-easy | queue-stale-unassigned | queue-stale-unassigned | all-ready-to-merge | stale-ready-to-merge | stale-delegated | stale-maintainer-merge | tech-debt | needs-decision | needs-merge | inessential-CI-fails | stale-new-contributor | needs-owner | other-base | from-fork | bad-title | unlabelled | contradictory-labels | approved | all

Overall statistics

Found 1267 open PRs overall. Among these PRs
  • 173 (13.7%) are awaiting review (these ones), among these 27 (15.6%) by new contributors (these ones)
  • 225 (17.8%) are blocked on another PR
  • 112 (8.8%) are awaiting the PR author's action
  • 168 (13.3%) have a merge conflict: among these, 56 (33.3%) would be ready for review otherwise: these
  • 37 (2.9%) are labelled help-wanted or please-adopt (roughly these)
  • 522 (41.2%) are marked as draft or work in progress
  • 3 (0.2%) are awaiting the outcome of a zulip discussion (these ones)
  • 5 (0.4%) are opened from a fork of mathlib (these ones)
  • 1 (0.1%) have contradictory labels (these ones)
  • 15 (1.2%) are delegated (stale ones are here)
  • 6 (0.5%) have been sent to bors (stale ones are here)
